614:\"<p>If you&#8217;re building an online community, then there is a good chance you are considering adding a forum to your website to allow users to enter into discussions with each other. We&#8217;ve noticed a lot of blog posts recommending outdated, no longer supported or non-forum solutions in their &#8220;best forum plugins&#8221; articles. So to help&#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://ultimatemember.com/top-4-forum-plugins-for-wordpress-in-2019/\">Top 4 forum plugins for WordPress in 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://ultimatemember.com\">Ultimate Member</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Calum Allison\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6255:\"\n<p>If you&#8217;re building an online community, then there is a good chance you are considering adding a forum to your website to allow users to enter into discussions with each other.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ve noticed a lot of blog posts recommending outdated, no longer supported or non-forum solutions in their &#8220;best forum plugins&#8221; articles.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So to help you decide which forum plugin to use on your WordPress website we&#8217;ve created this post to give you a quick overview of the best forum plugins in 2019.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>1. ForumWP</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forumwp-1024x561.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-753515\" srcset=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forumwp-1024x561.png 1024w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forumwp-300x164.png 300w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forumwp-768x421.png 768w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forumwp-265x145.png 265w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forumwp-530x291.png 530w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forumwp.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Most modern design and user experience</li><li>Inherits theme styling</li><li>Lightweight and fast</li><li>Built by same developers of Ultimate Member with integration with Ultimate Member via the free <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/um-forumwp/\">ForumWP extension</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Recently released so does not currently have as wide a feature set as offered by the other plugins</li><li>No free plan if you are only using free plugins on your website</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://forumwpplugin.com/\">View plugin</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h4>2. bbPress</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bbpress-1024x561.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-753516\" srcset=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bbpress-1024x561.png 1024w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bbpress-300x164.png 300w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bbpress-768x420.png 768w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bbpress-265x145.png 265w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bbpress-530x290.png 530w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bbpress.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Most used forum plugin, with over 300,000 active installs</li><li>Simple to install and use</li><li>Lightweight and fast</li><li>Integrated with Ultimate Member with <a href=\"https://ultimatemember.com/extensions/bbpress/\">paid extension</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Outdated design and user experience</li><li>No guaranteed support</li><li>bbPress addons are made by different developers. Many are outdated and not supported</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bbpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">View plugin</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h4>3. wpForo</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforo-1024x561.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-753517\" srcset=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforo-1024x561.png 1024w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforo-300x164.png 300w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforo-768x421.png 768w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforo-265x145.png 265w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforo-530x291.png 530w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforo.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Various layouts to choose from</li><li>Integration with Ultimate Member via their plugin</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Amount of settings can be overwhelming</li><li>Does not follow default wp-admin interface</li><li>Does not inherit theme styling</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforo/\" rel=\"nofollow\">View plugin</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h4>4. Asgaros Forum</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/asgaros-1024x561.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-753518\" srcset=\"https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/asgaros-1024x561.png 1024w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/asgaros-300x164.png 300w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/asgaros-768x421.png 768w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/asgaros-265x145.png 265w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/asgaros-530x291.png 530w, https://ultimatemember.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/asgaros.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Simple forum plugin</li><li>Lightweight and fast</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Does not follow default wp-admin interface</li><li>Does not inherit theme styling</li><li>Does not integrate with Ultimate Member</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/asgaros-forum/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>View plugin</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Summary</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are using Ultimate Member on your website we would recommend using either <a href=\"https://forumwpplugin.com/\">ForumWP</a> or bbPress as we have built native integrations for these plugins via our own extensions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>ForumWP is the best option if you don&#8217;t mind paying for plugins and are looking for a forum plugin that has the deepest integration with Ultimate Member.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you can only use a free plugin on your website then bbPress will still work fine with Ultimate Member.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://ultimatemember.com/top-4-forum-plugins-for-wordpress-in-2019/\">Top 4 forum plugins for WordPress in 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://ultimatemember.com\">Ultimate Member</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"ForumWP Giveaway – Win a free license\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0